Login/create new users

- set public/ private profiles and/or gardens

CRUD:

CREATE:

- user profile: public/private
- user garden(s): public/private
- growing session - a plant within a garden


READ:

- See all the user's plants
- See all the plants in a user's garden
- Search by plant name to see the optimal conditions required to grow
- See all the possible growing conditions (so the user sees the things needed to consider before growing)
- most popular plant
- see user's growing history
- OPTIONAL: difficulty aspect

UPDATE:

- update plant status/ number of plants in a garden by creating a growing session
- update user profile (bio, country, password, expertise)

DELETE:

- delete a growing session if plant dies
- delete profile
- delete a garden (optional)

